# BBS Firewall - IP Blocklist
#
# IPs listed here are permanently blocked from connecting.
# This is separate from the temporary blocks applied by rate limiting.
#
# One entry per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Supports single IPs and CIDR ranges.
#
# Examples:
#   192.168.1.100
#   10.0.0.0/24
#   2001:db8::1
#
# To use this file:
# 1. Copy to blocklist.txt
# 2. Add the IPs/ranges to block
# 3. Set BLOCKLIST_PATH=./blocklist.txt in your .env file

# 203.0.113.0
# 198.51.100.0
